00473 bool lequeal(Elem * a, Elem *b) {
00474     string typeA = a->whois();
00475     string typeB = b->whois();
00476 
00477     if (typeA.compare(typeB) != 0) { // nejsou stejne
00478         TypeException e;
00479         e.line = a->line;
00480         e.desc = strformat("Function == needs all parameters with same type. (%s vs. %s)",
00481                 typeA.c_str(), typeB.c_str());
00482 
00483         throw e;
00484     }
00485 
00486     bool result;
00487     if (typeA == "int") {
00488         result = ((expect_LInt(a)->repr) == (expect_LInt(b)->repr));
00489     }
00490 
00491     if (typeA == "symbol") {
00492         result = false;
00493     }
00494 
00495     if (typeA == "list") {
00496         LList * LA = expect_LList(a);
00497         LList * LB = expect_LList(b);
00498 
00499         if (LA->len() != LB->len()) {
00500             return false;
00501         }
00502 
00503         while (LA) {
00504             try {
00505                 if (!lequeal(LA->car, LB->car)) {
00506                     return false;
00507                 }
00508             } catch (TypeException) {
00509                 // sem se to dostane kdyz pri porovnavani seznamu narazime na stejny pozici na
00510                 // prvky s jinym typem: je to OK => bez vyjimky, a seznamy jsou rozdilne
00511                 return false;
00512             }
00513             LA = LA->cdr;
00514             LB = LB->cdr;
00515         }
00516         result = true;
00517     }
00518 
00519     if (typeA == "string") {
00520         LString* SA = expect_LString(a);
00521         LString* SB = expect_LString(b);
00522         result = SA->repr == SB->repr;
00523     }
00524 
00525     if (typeA == "functionC") {
00526         result = a == b;
00527     }
00528 
00529     if (typeA == "functionL") {
00530         result = a == b;
00531     }
00532     if (typeA == "LFunctionM") {
00533         result = a == b;
00534     }
00535 
00536     if (typeA == "bool") {
00537         result = ((dynamic_cast<LBool*> (a)->val) == (dynamic_cast<LBool*> (b)->val));
00538     }
00539 
00540     return result;
00541 }
